{"tid":2431180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何栢良：已幫家人登記接種復必泰 安全高效","createTime":"2021-03-03T12:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T13:46:12.000Z","uid":105567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e87eda13a830f61aff6833f2eed145062c8ceed1","tid":2431180,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"何栢良指，英國及美國目前已有過千萬人接種復必泰疫苗，根據英國政府最新公布分析成效數據，暫未經同行審批及在醫學期刊發表，但文件已能在網上查閱。當地750萬名70歲或以上人士，在去年12月至上月底接種疫苗，大部分是復必泰，整體成效達到85至90%；80歲以上，成效也有89%。他指即使是流感疫苗，也很少能有這樣高的成效，故認為是很好的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n至於一名63歲男子在接種科興疫苗後兩天死亡的個案，何栢良指英美每5至10萬人接種復必泰疫苗，亦會有1宗死亡個案，反映存在自然死亡機率，又認為內地及其他地方已累計逾1,000萬人接種科興疫苗，若有問題應顯然而見。他呼籲市民不應「自己嚇自己」，兩種疫苗都很安全，而復必泰疫苗則是既安全且高度有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%EF%BD%9C%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%B9%AB%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E5%BE%A9%E5%BF%85%E6%B3%B0-%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88-258017?fbclid=IwAR2lPnyCwldMQiDTJswAHOr1gCW0nwZizZdybvsFS5WKJXMLzSBgVquxNts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25EF%25BD%259C%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%2589%25AF%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25BF%2585%25E6%25B3%25B0-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2595%2588-258017%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2lPnyCwldMQiDTJswAHOr1gCW0nwZizZdybvsFS5WKJXMLzSBgVquxNts&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e9a99987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%EF%BD%9C%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%B9%AB%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E5%BE%A9%E5%BF%85%E6%B3%B0-%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88-258017?fbclid=IwAR2lPny